WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:48.041 --> 00:00:52.111
Fold in half

00:01:15.248 --> 00:01:22.846
Bring the top left corner to the center crease

00:01:35.014 --> 00:01:40.224
Valley-fold the top right corner

00:01:51.581 --> 00:01:53.753
Unfold

00:01:54.685 --> 00:02:00.397
Fold the bottom edge along the crease you just made

00:02:09.604 --> 00:02:16.844
Fold the top edge along the center crease

00:02:33.877 --> 00:02:41.723
Bring the left side tip to meet the center crease

00:02:42.595 --> 00:02:44.185
Unfold

00:02:44.522 --> 00:02:49.106
Inside reverse-fold

00:02:58.554 --> 00:03:04.841
Fold the right side under the left side

00:03:08.056 --> 00:03:10.666
One unit finished, To make the Trinity Box we need 3 units.

00:03:16.952 --> 00:03:25.933
To match the 3 pieces insert the short flap into the pocket of other unit

00:03:40.354 --> 00:03:48.809
Insert the loose flap from one unit under the flap of the unit next to it

00:04:07.636 --> 00:04:12.135
Trinity Box Done!

